  "description": "<p>A slim, stable reservoir that turns inside out for complete and easy cleaning. The locking centre baffle helps it sit flat against your back, and keeps it from slumping as you drink the contents down. If you need more carrying capacity, unlock the baffle to add another 0.5L of liquid. For cleaning and drying, unzip the baffle seal and reverse the reservoir.</p><ul><li>Made of lightweight TPU that's BPA-free</li><li>Wide sliding top opening is easy to use and allows rapid refills</li><li>Top grip handles to hold while filling</li><li>Silicone bite valve has an on/off switch to prevents leaks</li><li>High flow hose lets you drink more</li><li>Plug-N-Play connector lets you remove the hose quickly</li><li>Internal Shape-Shift baffle adds stability to reduce sloshing but unlocks to expand the volume or turn the reservoir inside out for easy cleaning and drying</li></ul>",
